    {
      "name": "rsvp",
      "docs": [
        "RSVP yes / no / maybe to an event. The Rsvp PDA seeded by",
        "(event, attendee) has an `init` constraint, so each TID can",
        "only RSVP once per event. Use `update_rsvp` to change a",
        "previous response."
      ],
      "discriminator": [
        134,
        164,
        221,
        33,
        183,
        12,
        73,
        32
      ],
      "accounts": [
        {
          "name": "event",
          "writable": true,
          "pda": {
            "seeds": [
              {
                "kind": "const",
                "value": [
                  101,
                  118,
                  101,
                  110,
                  116
                ]
              },
              {
                "kind": "account",
                "path": "event.creator",
                "account": "Event"
              },
              {
                "kind": "account",
                "path": "event.event_id",
                "account": "Event"
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "rsvp_record",
          "docs": [
            "`init` is the one-RSVP-per-TID guard: a second RSVP from the",
            "same wallet on the same event fails because the PDA already",
            "exists. To change a response, use `update_rsvp`."
          ],
          "writable": true,
          "pda": {
            "seeds": [
              {
                "kind": "const",
                "value": [
                  114,
                  115,
                  118,
                  112
                ]
